Keepin' The Faith: Momma's Got A Boyfriend - Sylvia is a successful, fifty year old California mother and widow, who is persuaded by her educated daughter Karen, to take a well deserved, first-class vacation to Mexico. Sylvia decides to surprise Karen by having her twenty-five year old boyfriend, Mike, tag along.

2010
Stars: Ro' Black, Blaise Brooks, Lala Costa
